Package effects

Class Effect

java.lang.Object
effects.Effect
Direct Known Subclasses:
BuildersGuildEffect, CoinCardEffect, ColoredCardResourceEffect, CopyOneGuildEffect, FreeCardPerAgeEffect, PlaySeventhCardEffect, ResourceChoiceEffect, ScienceChoiceEffect, ShipOwnersGuildEffect, StrategistsGuildEffect, TookDiscardCardEffect, TradeResourceEffect
public abstract class Effect
extends java.lang.Object
This class is just used as an abstraction level to define what special effects a card can have. Those effects range from choosing between two resources on a card, to having to pay only one coin for trading resources with your neighbors.
